''Prerequisite:'' [[Berserker Rage]].

While in a berserker rage, you cannot be [[charm]]ed, frightened, or otherwise magically compelled, and you are resistant to [[psychic damage|damage type]]. If you are charmed or frightened when you enter your rage, the effect is suspended for the duration of the rage.